body:
If you'd like to make a change, please feel free to send a pull request :)
Alternatively, you could use [`tf.logging.set_verbosity(tf.logging.WARN)`](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/logging/set_verbosity) to avoid any `logging.info` messages from showing up.

Hope that helps.
